headline: CDW’s Q4 Earnings Call: Our Top 5 Analyst Questions
summary: CDW’s Q4 results were greeted with a positive market reaction, reflecting stronger-than-anticipated demand across key IT categories. Management attributed the quarter’s momentum to double-digit growth in cloud, software, and professional services, as well as robust expansion in small business and education segments.
